The Brisbane Convention & Exhibition Centre is a convention facility in Queensland , Australia . It is located on the site of the former Interstate railway station in South Brisbane near the South Bank Parklands . The building is adjacent to South Brisbane Railway Station , and close to the Cultural Centre Busway Station . Officially opened in June 1995 , the Brisbane Convention & Exhibition Centre is used as a conference and convention venue and to hold exhibitions , as well as staging concerts . Featured artists who have appeared at the Centre include the Australian Pop - folk group The Seekers . The centre is also the ' home base ' for the Brisbane Bullets of Australia 's National Basketball League . It also hosted Equitana 2002 , an international equestrian event . The building is to be extended , with the construction of the extension being expected to take about two years to complete . You can help by expanding it . 